{"id":"api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse","title":"withNoDomReuse","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser\", \"name\": \"@angular/platform-browser\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse\", \"name\": \"withNoDomReuse\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/platform-browser\">@angular/platform-browser</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/platform-browser/src/hydration.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L51-L92\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/platform-browser/src/hydration.ts#L51-L92\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"withnodomreuse\">withNoDomReuse<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse#withnodomreuse\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    <label class=\"api-status-label dev-preview\" title=\"This API is in Developer Preview\">\n      <a href=\"guide/releases#developer-preview\">developer preview</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">在水合期间禁用 DOM 节点重用。有效地使 Angular 在客户端从头开始重新渲染应用程序。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Disables DOM nodes reuse during hydration. Effectively makes\nAngular re-render an application from scratch on the client.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse#description\">查看\"说明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse\" class=\"code-anchor\">withNoDomReuse</a></span>(): <a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeatureKind#NoDomReuseFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeatureKind.NoDomReuseFeature</a>&gt;</code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h6>\n  <p>没有参数。</p>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeature</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/platform-browser/HydrationFeatureKind#NoDomReuseFeature\" class=\"code-anchor\">HydrationFeatureKind.NoDomReuseFeature</a>&gt;</code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code></p></li>\n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/router/withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation\" class=\"code-anchor\">withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation</a></code></p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">启用此选项后，请确保通过在 <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code> 调用中使用 <code><a href=\"api/router/withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation\" class=\"code-anchor\">withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation</a></code> 将路由器的初始导航选项配置为 <code>enabledBlocking</code>：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When this option is enabled, make sure that the initial navigation\noption is configured for the Router as <code>enabledBlocking</code> by using the\n<code><a href=\"api/router/withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation\" class=\"code-anchor\">withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation</a></code> in the <code><a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a></code> call:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(RootComponent, {\n  providers: [\n    <a href=\"api/router/provideRouter\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideRouter</a>(\n      // ... other features ...\n      <a href=\"api/router/withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation\" class=\"code-anchor\">withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation</a>()\n    ),\n    <a href=\"api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideClientHydration</a>(<a href=\"api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse\" class=\"code-anchor\">withNoDomReuse</a>())\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">这将确保在 Router 中的所有异步操作（例如组件的延迟加载、等待异步守卫和解析器）完成后重新渲染应用程序，以避免过早清除客户端上的 DOM，从而导致内容闪烁。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This would ensure that the application is rerendered after all async\noperations in the Router (such as lazy-loading of components,\nwaiting for async guards and resolvers) are completed to avoid\nclearing the DOM on the client too soon, thus causing content flicker.</p>\n\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/platform-browser\n - api/platform-browser/HydrationFeature\n - api/platform-browser/HydrationFeatureKind#NoDomReuseFeature\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - api/platform-browser/provideClientHydration\n - api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse#description\n - api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse#see-also\n - api/platform-browser/withNoDomReuse#withnodomreuse\n - api/router/provideRouter\n - api/router/withEnabledBlockingInitialNavigation\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/platform-browser/src/hydration.ts?message=docs(platform-browser)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L51-L92\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/platform-browser/src/hydration.ts#L51-L92\n-->"}